# --- Secrets / local config -------------------------------------------------
# NEVER commit the wallet address. It is not a cryptographic secret, but it is
# a permanent, public, on-chain identifier: committing it here links this repo
# (and your GitHub identity) to your full Polymarket betting history forever.
# It lives in data/*.db and .env only. Both are ignored below.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
.streamlit/secrets.toml
wallet.txt
*.wallet

# --- Local database ---------------------------------------------------------
# checkpoints are personal betting history; never commit them
data/*.db
data/*.db-journal
data/*.db-wal
data/*.db-shm
data/*.sqlite
data/*.sqlite3

# --- Exports ----------------------------------------------------------------
exports/
*.csv
*.png
!docs/**/*.png

